title: Vegan Supper Club - temporarily closed
description: A 100% vegan five course meal using organic local produce prepared by Chef Stephan Black. Meet other diners and share a table in a stunning location set amongst the gardens and rice fields of Azadi in Pejeng, a short drive from Arjuna statue, in Ubud at the eastern end of Jl Raya. A suggested donation of 300,000 IDR on the night is asked. Space is limited so please contact to book your place at the table. Runs every week. May 2015, reported that club was on hold, please update HappyCow of changes.
